Generates egg reloads. petCount is how many mobs the egg should spawn. Power is a strength value given to the pet mob. If the power is very high, egg will have large reloads and vice-versa. MinUseTime is the minimum hatch time to increase the rarity of the spawned pet. If hatch time goes below that, rarity of the pet is increased. In simpler words, if the cutoff is large, eggs will very easily spawn high rarity pets.
